{"tid":1234863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千奇唔好分化 勇武派同和理非一定要團結","createTime":"2019-06-17T04:18:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T07:42:42.000Z","uid":215417,"like":193,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"f07edc3ba433e7ef0822382571ee617823d27939","tid":1234863,"uid":215417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:18:05.000Z","msg":"今朝睇左各位巴絲既post <br />\n發現多左好多分化post<br />\n有人指責民主黨 又有人指責民陣大台<br />\n但係係呢個時候我地絕唔可以分化 <br />\n政府想做既就係要拖延 慢慢咁樣退半步 <br />\n令民怨漸漸減少<br />\n如果係呢個時候我地再搞分化 就注定會失敗<br />\n所以大家都係繼續張槍頭指向政府<br />\n要求政府釋放義士 撤回暴動定性先<br />\n再講一次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好分化呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"ce04815664332c2707f1458cccf6ab46e7847229","tid":1234863,"uid":215417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:18:14.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2fd3d1d610e9a0b9b9e6fe66f9912afb0dcb6ae7","tid":1234863,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f937dbb9345ef261cffc330d53d3f8fe0465bad","tid":1234863,"uid":45046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:18:30.000Z","msg":"唔想變雨傘2.0嘅入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1234083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1234083</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n希望你地可以分享俾多啲人睇 警方已經轉左玩法今朝冇清到場 就係為左要去返雨傘咁要團體向法院提出清場 但如果用我方法可以令返主導權同埋迫到政府官員出面回應 甚至民生問題都可以用依個方法到時係選舉拎返地方票"},{"pid":"c7658e1a6b6815463aa913e965ac8e41c25a08f5","tid":1234863,"uid":215417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:18:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e81f7f7dd4a9fb3a7a44d72db613df238c069019","tid":1234863,"uid":215417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:19:21.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983a78315af2b938c5e90e8955f51ef183c1fe6a","tid":1234863,"uid":215417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T04:19:59.